These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
7 different games are played: backgammon, poker, scrabble, whist, go, monopoly, billiard
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, british, chinese, dutch, egyptian, french, german
There are 7 different favourite colors: pink, lilac, grey, orange, mauve, yellow, amber
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, subway, train, van
 1. the person who likes orange is on the far right##1
 2. the person who likes mauve is the dutch##1
 3. the person driving the subway is the person who likes grey##1
 4. the british is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the german##1
 6. the person playing poker is the person who likes grey##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the right of the egyptian##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the van and the french##2
 9. the egyptian is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the person playing scrabble is in the middle##1
11. the person who likes pink is the person playing go##1
12. the person playing go is the person driving the bike##1
13. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the chinese##1
14. the french is the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person driving the train is on the left of the german##1
16. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
17. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the chinese##1
18. the person playing billiard is on the right of the egyptian##1
19. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Game      | poker  | monopoly        | go | scrabble      | whist     | backgammon      | billiard     |
| Nationality   | british | dutch         | german   | australian | french    | egyptian | chinese |
| Color         | grey | mauve | pink | lilac | amber  | yellow  | orange    |
| Transport     | subway  | train         | bike     | jet-ski    | quad-bike | ship     | van     |

